languages.text:
The Overseer immediately dashes to their familiar within {uip|Cells|ef69d99ee41d49f1bef7a6194f78dd38} cells. The Overseer can move through allies and enemies but not through obstacles. This movement does not provoke attacks of opportunity.
If the familiar is the {g|f:ec56854df2e84ef196a49079a43b5211}soaring{/g} cyber-eagle, the Overseer gains +{uip|Cells|ef69d99ee41d49f1bef7a6194f78dd38} MP instead.

languages.text:
Der {g|Encyclopedia:CareerOverseerGlossary}Aufseher{/g} läuft in einem Radius von {uip|Cells|ef69d99ee41d49f1bef7a6194f78dd38} Feldern sofort zu seinem Vertrauten. Ist der Vertraute ein {g|f:ec56854df2e84ef196a49079a43b5211}kreisender{/g} Cyber-Adler, erhält der Aufseher stattdessen +{uip|Cells|ef69d99ee41d49f1bef7a6194f78dd38} {g|Encyclopedia:MovementPoints}BP{/g}.

Le {g|Encyclopedia:CareerOverseerGlossary}surveillant{/g} rejoint immédiatement son familier à une distance maximale de {uip|Cells|ef69d99ee41d49f1bef7a6194f78dd38} cases.
